{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendpurchase:withprice:currencycode:anddate:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendPurchase:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"productIdentifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"withPrice:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDecimalNumber","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDecimalNumber"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"price","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"currencyCode:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"currencyCode","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"andDate:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDate"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"date","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"productIdentifier","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The product identifier (SKU).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purchase price as NSDecimalNumber for precision."}]}],"name":"price"},{"name":"currencyCode","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"ISO 4217 currency code (e.g., “USD”, “EUR”, “GBP”)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"date","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The date when the purchase occurred.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Manually track a purchase when you need more control than automatic"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"StoreKit tracking, or when processing purchases from other sources","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(web purchases, promotional codes, etc.).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this for:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Non-StoreKit purchases (web, third-party payment processors)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Custom price tracking (discounts, promotions)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Server-verified purchases","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Cross-platform purchase sync","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Track purchases from different sources:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class PurchaseTracker {","","    func trackStoreKitPurchase(_ transaction: SKPaymentTransaction, product: SKProduct) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendPurchase(","            product.productIdentifier,","            withPrice: product.price,","            currencyCode: product.priceLocale.currencyCode ?? \"USD\",","            andDate: transaction.transactionDate ?? Date()","        )","","        updatePurchaseTags(productId: product.productIdentifier, price: product.price)","    }","","    func trackWebPurchase(_ purchase: WebPurchase) {","        \/\/ Track purchase made through web checkout","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendPurchase(","            purchase.productId,","            withPrice: NSDecimalNumber(value: purchase.amount),","            currencyCode: purchase.currency,","            andDate: purchase.timestamp","        )","","        updatePurchaseTags(productId: purchase.productId,","                          price: NSDecimalNumber(value: purchase.amount))","    }","","    func trackPromotionalPurchase(productId: String, originalPrice: Decimal, discountedPrice: Decimal) {","        \/\/ Track discounted purchase","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendPurchase(","            productId,","            withPrice: NSDecimalNumber(decimal: discountedPrice),","            currencyCode: Locale.current.currencyCode ?? \"USD\",","            andDate: Date()","        )","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"used_promotion\": true,","            \"discount_amount\": NSDecimalNumber(decimal: originalPrice - discountedPrice)","        ])","    }","","    private func updatePurchaseTags(productId: String, price: NSDecimalNumber) {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"total_purchases\": incrementPurchaseCount(),","            \"total_spent\": calculateTotalSpent(adding: price),","            \"customer_tier\": determineCustomerTier()","        ])","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"sendPurchase:withPrice:currencyCode:andDate:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendPurchase:withPrice:currencyCode:andDate:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"sendPurchase:withPrice:currencyCode:andDate:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendPurchase:withPrice:currencyCode:andDate:"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendPurchase:withPrice:currencyCode:andDate:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/doc